    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love the moment you see it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is an exceptional example of a high-revving, naturally aspirated masterpiece. Featuring a 3.8L flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, this specimen offers unparalleled tactile feedback. The mechanical integrity is flawless, with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and an active suspension management system that provides razor-sharp turn-in and cornering stability. The valvetrain is silent, the compression is optimal across all cylinders, and the chassis remains rigid with zero bush deflection or fluid seepage. This is a concours-level machine for the purist who demands a turn-key performance vehicle with zero mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented here is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or sun-fading. The paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the leather seats are supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the original 'new car' scent is still present. Every button, switch, and electronic system functions with the crispness of a brand-new vehicle. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with all service performed by master technicians using only OEM parts. A complete binder of service history, original window sticker, and two sets of keys are included. This is a collector-grade example that drives as flawlessly as the day it was delivered.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
